DISCIPLINARY DOCKET

99-1559. Columbus Bar Assn. v. Reed.

On September 15, 1999, respondent filed a request for extension of time to file objections that were due by September 14,1999. Accordingly,

IT IS ORDERED by the court, sua sponte, that respondent’s request for extension of time to file objections be, and hereby is, stricken.
